###############################################################################
### NOTES
###############################################################################

# 1. Token Expiration: Tokens expire after 1 hour
#    If you get "Token has expired!", login again to get a new token
#
# 2. Update @authToken: After logging in, copy the auth_token from the
#    response and paste it into the @authToken variable at the top
#
# 3. Database State: These tests may create data in your database.
#    You may want to clear test data between runs.
#
# 4. Password Security: Remember that passwords are stored in plain text
#    in this educational implementation. In production, use bcrypt!
#
# 5. Rate Limiting: If you have Assignment 6's rate limiting enabled,
#    you may hit rate limits. Wait or restart the server to reset.
